//
//
// CUSTOM VIEW KEYS/IDENTIFIERS:
// -> tabs: The tab items
// item -> title: The title of a tab
// item -> iconWidthRatio: The ratio of the width of icon to tab's width
// item -> iconWidthRatioSelected: The ratio of the width of icon to selected tab's width
// item -> composite: The composite of the title of tab
// item -> compositeSelected: The composite of the title of selected tab
// item -> icon: The image of the icon of the tab
// item -> iconSelected: The image of the icon of the selected tab
// item -> background: The background image of the tab
// item -> backgroundSelected: The background image of the selected tab
//
// -> xScaleRatio: Ratio of selected tab's width to a tab's
// -> yScaleRatio: Ratio of selected tab's height to a tab's
// -> widthByHeightRatio: The ratio of width of the tab bar to its height
// -> coverBackground: The background of the dashboard screens (works if background is a cover image or panoramic image)
// -> background: The background of the dashboard screens (works if background is supposed to be common)
//
//

